The following message is available to read some of the forecourt controller parameters. All the parameters in a set are read.
For grade-assigned parameters, all parameters(for each defined grade) are returned if NoFcPars is set ZERO in the request message
CODE: 0BH SUBC: 00H DATA: FcParGroupId + FcParSetId + [NoFcPars | ZERO] + NoFcPars { FcParId }

The following message is used to read a set of prices in the Forecourt Controller.
All prices in the price-bank are returned with the following format

DATA:   UserId +
        FcPriceSetId +
        NoFcPriceGroups +
        NoFcGrades +
         NoFcPriceGroups
         {
            FcPriceGroupId
         }
         NoFcGrades
         {
            FcGradeId
         }
         NoFcPriceGroups
         {
           NoFcGrades
           {
              Price_e
           }
         } +
        [FcPriceSetDateAndTime | PriceSetActivationDateAndTime]

            Tipo de mensaje no solicitado

{

 EXTC +

 SUBC

}
